        <updateDate>2012-11-15T13:59:54Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Nuclear Reactor Safety First Act - Amends the Atomic Energy Act of 1954 to prohibit the Nuclear Regulatory Commission (NRC) from approving the renewal of a nuclear reactor license if the renewal application was submitted more than 10 years before the license's expiration.</p> <BR>]]></text>
      </summary>
